This review is for the Take Care Clinic inside this particular Walgreens location.
If 2 1/2 hour waits just to be told we don't treat that sort of issue here is what you want to be told, this is the clinic for you.
If you want a nurse practictioner who doesn't read the notes you leave on the check in screen, this is the place for you as well.
Health care in Las Vegas already has a less than sterling reputation.
Clinics like this one are definitely a contributing factor.
I will pay the premium for Urgent Care services and avoid this place like the plague.

